data.name: DataGridView1.ToolTip
data.value:
Hidden layers: 1 hidden layer: linear seperable functions/decisions; approximate any function containing a continuous mapping from one finite space to another. 2 hidden layers: arbitrary decision boundarys to arbitrary accuracy with rational activation functions; aproximate any smooth mapping to any accuracy.
Hidden neurons: Between the size of the input layer and the size of the output layer. 2/3 the size of the input layer + size of the output layer. Less than twice the size of the input layer.
Activation function: Sigmoid returns values from 0 to 1. Hyperbolic tangent returns values from -1 to 1.
